\n<br />\n其實原本個team 已經夠人， run 得好好 <br />\n係老細無啦啦又話想請人<br />\n結果請左我 ， 但又勁小野做， 痴能線 <br />\n工程果行"},{"pid":"318fad467a7c8089379be04282278cb33a368e4f","tid":111800,"uid":33866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:24:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用空餘時間睇書學下投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想咁得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 又唔可以明目張膽睇"},{"pid":"b5c1b46c5fc0f7e2f0ffe50eef8763de8c3813ad","tid":111800,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>廿幾k 冇野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵緊工，不過可以慢慢揀先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n廿幾先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上到30k+又冇野做就正</blockquote><br />\n廿中"},{"pid":"4e32ced8ea43a43119c9557ad064e98c6edfff8a","tid":111800,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用空餘時間睇書學下投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想咁得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇野做，但係又唔可以拎書出黎睇咁串。<br />\n長玩電話，塞單邊耳聽歌都仲可以"},{"pid":"365efe1c73bdbcec3d21c6c0ca55aa0e9f81de59","tid":111800,"uid":3186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:36:40.000Z","msg":"我試過簽左份傻仔contract賠一個月人工都照走<br />\n亦都試過做既野太悶而走<br />\n<br />\n第一份真係頭果幾日 日日都問佢有咩比我做<br />\n問到我下定決心走都無野做<br />\n<br />\n第二份就係日日都做啲好簡單既野，好似打字員咁<br />\n<br />\n利申：IT狗"},{"pid":"24dde5c57111ee21cde39166e7d5b74ed1962ded","tid":111800,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:36:45.000Z","msg":"咁搞笑"},{"pid":"edaf512716cfb066d28ad8d1daffa932b9e41d65","tid":111800,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:59:46.000Z","msg":"返緊hea 到傻嘅工覆呢個post 中，朝早做15分鐘嘢後就等食飯，飯後做一兩個鐘就等收工<br />\n<br />\n人工12k 打算星期六日會返埋part time"},{"pid":"186d2a7625a9dc10edd80e7e430fc17b3442d526","tid":111800,"uid":65640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:06:35.000Z","msg":"以前同你一樣<br />\n無人教，無人會俾野你做<br />\n上網又唔俾，公司啲文件都俾我睇晒<br />\n日日反工就係坐監<br />\n同人講，人地會覺得好正咁<br />\n真相係時間過得慢，又無存在感，不過我人事ok<br />\n<br />\n最後都轉左工，一路做只會繼續乜都唔識<br />\n幾年後轉工，你都仲係白紙"},{"pid":"f1a6b65c52e79681d7b43f5f3e01af4b9db5f22a","tid":111800,"uid":49642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:08:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實可唔可以講下你地份職責係做咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實原本個team 已經夠人， run 得好好 <br />\n係老細無啦啦又話想請人<br />\n結果請左我 ， 但又勁小野做， 痴能線 <br />\n工程果行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你老細有head count梗係請左個人番黎先<br />\n唔岩使大不了換<br />\n到時忙起上黎HR又唔批head count <br />\n佢咪GG"},{"pid":"ac4533aa82341f97e9ceac21d85e73da43e65e3a","tid":111800,"uid":52252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:11:37.000Z","msg":"8成時間無野做,一有野做就好多濕尻麻煩野<br />\n試過成日剩係send左封用1分鐘都唔駛既email<br />\n<br />\n想辭職,但一直搵唔到新工<br />\n<br />\n半專業,人工俾出面低,bonus算ok"},{"pid":"27e2fdba7773cab507a78d610ad7bf23e294841c","tid":111800,"uid":38102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:25:03.000Z","msg":"我好啲<br />\n<br />\n冇咩野做 <br />\n但比我上網 做功課 玩電話<br />\n偷偷地訓覺 打機 睇書 睇漫畫都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但真係好悶 我個位附近得我一個"},{"pid":"10c1c9096fc79bc62f5e4d173b7875dfac963cc6","tid":111800,"uid":56618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:30:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正苦d垃圾先係冗員之最<br />\n搵緊3 40k零工作量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓豬目標係呢d就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa42b4d779c52f5d5cda0fcd90c8f0928431d9e6","tid":111800,"uid":73972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>廿幾k 冇野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵緊工，不過可以慢慢揀先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n廿幾先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上到30k+又冇野做就正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你以為啦，無野做但要俾office困住其實好辛苦"},{"pid":"6a8f7080014bab94bcbc623a1b6d65c4c7871d93","tid":111800,"uid":79632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:43:54.000Z","msg":"正苦 19k 已經連續三日零工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945957e6ae51462c58cbd8fcd24537a0686565ce","tid":111800,"uid":25514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:00:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>廿幾k 冇野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵緊工，不過可以慢慢揀先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n廿幾先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上到30k+又冇野做就正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你以為啦，無野做但要俾office困住其實好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n坐監都有得打下羽毛波整下圖書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19068dec955e71e4733fad3b65f228de75c0f52e","tid":111800,"uid":20163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:00:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正苦 19k 已經連續三日零工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正苦咩post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576bee72fca209a12b7144bbc66ad57d46197a91","tid":111800,"uid":73783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:01:11.000Z","msg":"其實0工作量真係好辛苦<br />\n日日返工唔知做咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces